## 🟡 Medium — Missing Negative / Edge-Case Tests

No test covers **any** failure path or boundary condition:

| Missing test | What could break in prod |
|---|---|
| `UpdatePrice` on nonexistent SKU | Should throw `KeyNotFoundException` — untested |
| `GetProduct` with unknown SKU | Should return `null` — untested |
| `Search` with no matches | Could break callers expecting empty list |
| `ImportFromCsv` with malformed input | No validation exists; `IndexOutOfRange` in prod |
| `ApplyBulkDiscount` with fraction ≥ 1 | Would set negative prices — no guard, no test |
| `ExportToCsv` with commas in product names | CSV injection / parse round-trip failure |

